                            <comment id="115209" author="rread" created="Wed, 13 May 2015 17:04:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;No worries - I had to stare at it for a few minutes to convince myself it actually was as broken as I thought it was. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="115206" author="adilger" created="Wed, 13 May 2015 16:47:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;My bad, didn&apos;t read the code correctly... &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="115055" author="rread" created="Tue, 12 May 2015 18:23:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This also rejects LLAPI_LAYOUT_DEFAULT, too.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I noticed this problem while writing unit tests for my own tool. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="115053" author="pjones" created="Tue, 12 May 2015 18:16:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yang Sheng&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you please take care of this patch?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="115052" author="gerrit" created="Tue, 12 May 2015 18:11:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ned Bass (bass6@llnl.gov) uploaded a new patch: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/14784&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/14784&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
